{"comments":"Easing Preset Picker Component\n\nA dropdown selector for choosing from predefined easing curves. Displays\na mini preview of each easing and organizes them into categories.\n\n## Categories\n\n- Standard: linear, ease, ease-in, ease-out, ease-in-out\n- Sine: ease-in-sine, ease-out-sine, ease-in-out-sine\n- Quad: ease-in-quad, ease-out-quad, ease-in-out-quad\n- Cubic: ease-in-cubic, ease-out-cubic, ease-in-out-cubic\n- Quart: ease-in-quart, ease-out-quart, ease-in-out-quart\n- Quint: ease-in-quint, ease-out-quint, ease-in-out-quint\n- Expo: ease-in-expo, ease-out-expo, ease-in-out-expo\n- Circ: ease-in-circ, ease-out-circ, ease-in-out-circ\n- Back: ease-in-back, ease-out-back, ease-in-out-back\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Component.Motion.Curve.EasingPicker as EasingPicker\n\nHH.slot _easingPicker unit EasingPicker.component\n  { selected: Easing.easeInOut\n  , disabled: false\n  }\n  HandleEasingSelected\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"EasingPicker component\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"m","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"constraintAnn":[],"constraintArgs":[{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"constraintClass":[["Effect","Aff","Class"],"MonadAff"],"constraintData":null,"constraintKindArgs":[]},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Halogen","Component"],"Component"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Curve","EasingPicker"],"Query"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Curve","EasingPicker"],"Input"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Curve","EasingPicker"],"Output"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"c